window.bookSummaryJSON = "Here is the original American full dramatization of <i>The Hobbit</i>, as broadcast on National Public Radio. <p>Bilbo Baggins, a gentle hobbit who loves the comforts of home, reluctantly joins a company of dwarves on a journey to recover plundered gold from a fierce dragon. It's a tale of high adventure and astonishing courage, and a magical prelude to the <i>Lord of the Rings</i> trilogy.</p>"; 
